---
title: Chicken Schnitzel Katsu Curry & Rapid Rice with Creamy Slaw & Spring Onion
description: Warm, tart and sweet - all words we use to describe luscious katsu sauce, the superhero sidekick of Japanese cuisine! Pour it over a golden crumbed chicken schnitzel with fluffy rice, and watch as every bite becomes a delicious thrill ride.
